{"id":1926,"date":"2020-08-24T11:44:14","date_gmt":"2020-08-24T04:44:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=1926"},"modified":"2020-09-10T14:25:59","modified_gmt":"2020-09-10T07:25:59","slug":"our-present-our-future-vi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/our-present-our-future-vi\/","title":{"rendered":"Hi\u1ec7n T\u1ea1i T\u01b0\u01a1ng Lai"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47f6251q fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/caravellenight_1360x420.jpg 1360w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d3d6ddc4cd5faa2eb8669c734ed850ce_caravellenight_1360x420-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d3d6ddc4cd5faa2eb8669c734ed850ce_caravellenight_1360x420-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d3d6ddc4cd5faa2eb8669c734ed850ce_caravellenight_1360x420-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/d3d6ddc4cd5faa2eb8669c734ed850ce_caravellenight_1360x420-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/caravellenight_1360x420.jpg\" alt=\"Ho Chi Minh City at Night\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-48i4oqir fg-section fg-text-dark\" id=\"intro\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4oqis fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-48i4oqiv fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">HI\u1ec6N T\u1ea0I - T\u01af\u01a0NG LAI<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4oqj0 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Hi\u1ebfm kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n n&agrave;o c&oacute; c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i h&igrave;nh \u1ea3nh l&atilde;ng m\u1ea1n, d\u1ec5 m\u1ebfn v&agrave; d\u1ec5 h&igrave;nh dung nh\u01b0 The Caravelle &ndash; C&aacute;nh bu\u1ed3m. Thanh &acirc;m ng\u1ecdt ng&agrave;o c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb n&agrave;y g\u1ee3i ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfc thuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica, hay nh\u01b0 c&aacute;ch ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph&aacute;p g\u1ecdi ch&uacute;ng l&agrave; &ldquo;caravelle&rdquo;, nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc thuy\u1ec1n bu\u1ed3m h\u1ea1ng nh\u1eb9, ch\u1ea1y nhanh t\u1eeb th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 15, rong ru\u1ed5i tr&ecirc;n h\u1ea3i tr&igrave;nh kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 t&igrave;m ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i giao th\u01b0\u01a1ng, nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn th&aacute;m hi\u1ec3m, v&agrave; ch&acirc;n tr\u1eddi m\u1edbi. V&agrave; c&oacute; l\u1ebd kh&ocirc;ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi&ecirc;n m&agrave; h&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng Air France, c&ocirc;ng ty n\u1eafm c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n trong to&agrave; kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n ban \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1eb7t v\u0103n ph&ograve;ng t\u1ea1i \u0111&acirc;y ngay khi khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111&atilde; cho v\u1eadn h&agrave;nh lo\u1ea1i m&aacute;y bay ph\u1ea3n l\u1ef1c m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 c&oacute; c&ugrave;ng t&ecirc;n g\u1ecdi.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle chi\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb th\u1ebf trung t&acirc;m trong \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng x&atilde; h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i S&agrave;i G&ograve;n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u0103m 1959. N\u0103m 1998, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfn h&agrave;nh x&acirc;y d\u1ef1ng th&ecirc;m to&agrave; th&aacute;p 24 t\u1ea7ng b&ecirc;n c\u1ea1nh to&agrave; nh&agrave; 10 t\u1ea7ng ban \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1edbi t\u1ea7m nh&igrave;n bao qu&aacute;t th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 v&agrave; v\u1ecb tr&iacute; \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n Nh&agrave; H&aacute;t Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 h&agrave;o n\u1eb1m \u1edf trung t&acirc;m th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 t\u1eebng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l&agrave; H&ograve;n Ng\u1ecdc Vi\u1ec5n \u0110&ocirc;ng. Caravelle t\u1eebng l&agrave; m&aacute;i nh&agrave; c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u qu&acirc;n \u0111o&agrave;n b&aacute;o ch&iacute; qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 Chi\u1ebfn tranh Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m S&agrave;i G&ograve;n (nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l&agrave; Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh) c&oacute; th\u1ec3 coi l&agrave; t&acirc;m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch&uacute; &yacute; c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th&ocirc;ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng T&acirc;y khi nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ng&agrave;y nay, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle S&agrave;i G&ograve;n v\u1edbi c&aacute;c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm v\u1ecb tr&iacute; \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong l&ograve;ng th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1. L&agrave; m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n, mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho du kh&aacute;ch nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t khi l\u01b0u tr&uacute; t\u1ea1i S&agrave;i G&ograve;n, Caravelle \u0111&atilde; cho ti\u1ebfn h&agrave;nh d\u1ef1 &aacute;n n&acirc;ng c\u1ea5p to&agrave;n di\u1ec7n kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef v\u1ecb th\u1ebf kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-48i4oqir{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;}.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 ,.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:before,.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:after,.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *,.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:before,.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:after{ color: #490042 !important;}.ffb-id-48i4oqj0{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:before,.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:after,.ffb-id-48i4o