lle-Saigon-Signature-Studio-768-c-100.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle-Saigon-Signature-Studio.jpg\" alt=\"The Signature Studio room at Caravelle 5 Star Hotel Saigon, Vietnam\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48i4p66q fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">L\u01afU TR\u00da T\u1ea0I CARAVELLE<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4p66r fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cung c\u1ea5p m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; kh&oacute;i thu\u1ed1c l&aacute; trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c&aacute;c ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n. Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n c&oacute; hai t&ograve;a, m\u1ed9t to&agrave; Opera Wing v\u1edbi to&agrave;n c\u1ea3nh bao qu&aacute;t C&ocirc;ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng Lam S\u01a1n v&agrave; th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1, v&agrave; m\u1ed9t t&ograve;a Heritage Wing \u0111&atilde; \u0111i v&agrave;o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1959, v&agrave; l&agrave; m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1. D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d&agrave;n tr\u1ea3i trong c\u1ea3 hai t&ograve;a v&agrave; gi&uacute;p cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&oacute; th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v&agrave; c&oacute; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c&aacute;c l\u1ee3i &iacute;ch t\u1eeb S\u1ea3nh Signature.<\/p>\n<p>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc m\u1edf c\u1eeda v&agrave;o \u0110&ecirc;m Gi&aacute;ng Sinh n\u0103m 1959, Caravelle Saigon \u0111&atilde; tr\u1edf th&agrave;nh \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m cao c\u1ea5p, n\u01a1i di\u1ec5n ra m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1. N\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb tr&iacute; trung t&acirc;m, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c&aacute;c \u0111\u1ecba danh v&agrave; \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m mang t&iacute;nh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Nh&agrave; h&aacute;t Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1 S&agrave;i G&ograve;n, hay c&ograve;n g\u1ecdi l&agrave; Nh&agrave; H&aacute;t Th&agrave;nh Ph\u1ed1, Nh&agrave; Th\u1edd \u0110\u1ee9c B&agrave;, con ph\u1ed1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0110\u1ed3ng Kh\u1edfi, ph\u1ed1 \u0111i b\u1ed9 Nguy\u1ec5n Hu\u1ec7, v&agrave; Ch\u1ee3 B\u1ebfn Th&agrave;nh l&acirc;u \u0111\u1eddi.<\/p>\n<p>Ph&iacute;a sau b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; trung t&acirc;m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v&agrave; v\u0103n ho&aacute;, kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ch&iacute;nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nguy&ecirc;n b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 quan th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 1960s &ndash; kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n cao nh\u1ea5t v&agrave; hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4p66s buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"\/rooms-suites-vi\/\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-xs    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">XEM CHI TI\u1ebeT<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4p66t fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-el-has-bg fg-text-dark\"><span class=\"fg-bg\"><span data-fg-bg=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;color&quot;,&quot;opacity&quot;:1,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" class=\"fg-bg-layer fg-bg-type-color \" style=\"opacity: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\"><\/span><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-48i4p671 fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy.jpg 900w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/c7db6dfa2c771466ad022516ae8093db_Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/c7db6dfa2c771466ad022516ae8093db_Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy-768-c-100.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy.jpg\" alt=\"Caravelle1960s-with-Australian-Embassy\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48i4p672 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">TH\u00d4NG TIN TH\u00da V\u1eca<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4p673 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng v&agrave;o m&ugrave;a Gi&aacute;ng Sinh n\u0103m 1959, v&agrave; \u0111&atilde; tr\u1edf th&agrave;nh n\u01a1i t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c&aacute;c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp m\u1eb7t, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v&agrave; ti\u1ec7c d\u1ea1 v\u0169 sang tr\u1ecdng . K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111&oacute;, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n l&agrave; n\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy&ecirc;n ch&agrave;o \u0111&oacute;n c&aacute;c v\u1ecb nguy&ecirc;n th\u1ee7 cao c\u1ea5p, gi\u1edbi ch&iacute;nh tr\u1ecb gia v&agrave; c&aacute;c nh&acirc;n v\u1eadt n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>N\u0103m 1975, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle \u0111\u1ed5i t&ecirc;n l&agrave; kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n \u0110\u1ed9c L\u1eadp, m\u1eebng ng&agrave;y gi\u1ea3i ph&oacute;ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa th\u1eadp ni&ecirc;n 1990, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n t\u1ea1m ng\u01b0ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 x&acirc;y d\u1ef1ng th&ecirc;m to&agrave; th&aacute;p m\u1edbi cao 24 t\u1ea7ng v&agrave; ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 8 th&aacute;ng 5 n\u0103m 1998.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Saigon Saigon Bar, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b&igrave;nh ch\u1ecdn l&agrave; &ldquo;Qu&aacute;n Bar t\u1ea7ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t S&agrave;i G&ograve;n&rdquo;&nbsp; v&agrave; n\u1eb1m trong Top 10 \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u1ea3i tr&iacute; th&uacute; v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1, m\u1edf c\u1eeda t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1959 v&agrave; hi\u1ec7n nay v\u1eabn to\u1ea1 l\u1ea1c t\u1ea1i t\u1ea7ng 10 to&agrave; nh&agrave; \u0111\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n c\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n, qu&aacute;n bar v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng n&eacute;t \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng&agrave;y nay. N\u01a1i \u0111&acirc;y l&agrave; \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed1i trao \u0111\u1ed5i th&ocirc;ng tin ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n chi\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eddi \u0111&oacute;.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>N\u0103m 2001, kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n Caravelle vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111&oacute;n ti\u1ebfp \u0111o&agrave;n l&agrave;m phim v&agrave; n\u01a1i \u0111&acirc;y l&agrave; phim tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 phim n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 Tr\u1ea7m L\u1eb7ng&rdquo; chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ti\u1ec3u thuy\u1ebft c&ugrave;ng t&ecirc;n c\u1ee7a nh&agrave; v\u0103n Graham Greene, do di\u1ec5n vi&ecirc;n danh ti\u1ebfng Michael Caine th\u1ee7 vai ch&iacute;nh.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><style>.ffb-id-48i4oqir{ \npadding-top: 50px;\npadding-right: 50px;\npadding-bottom: 50px;\npadding-left: 50px;\n\n}\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 ,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:before,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:after,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:before,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:after{ \ncolor: #490042 !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:before,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:after,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:hover,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:focus,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:before,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:after,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:hover,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:focus{ \nfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0{ \nfont-size: 13px !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 ,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:before,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:after,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:hover,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0:focus,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:before,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:after,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:hover,\n.ffb-id-48i4oqj0 *:focus{ \nfont-size: 13px !important;\n}\n.ffb-id-48i4oqiv 