;color&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\" class=\"fg-bg-layer fg-bg-type-color \" style=\"opacity: 1; background-color: ;\"><\/span><\/span><h1 class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdc9 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">S\u1ee8 M\u1ec6NH, T\u1ea6M NH\u00ccN V\u00c0 GI\u00c1 TR\u1eca C\u1ee6A CARAVELLE<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdca fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdcd fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">S\u1ee8 M\u1ec6NH<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdce fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle l&agrave; l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti&ecirc;n c\u1ee7a du kh&aacute;ch:&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1eb1m \u1edf tr&aacute;i tim c\u1ee7a S&agrave;i G&ograve;n, du kh&aacute;ch c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0 l&agrave; th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n trong gia \u0111&igrave;nh Caravelle.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t l&ecirc;n ti&ecirc;u chu\u1ea9n 5 sao, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho du kh&aacute;ch d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1eadn t&acirc;m, chuy&ecirc;n nghi\u1ec7p v&agrave; ti\u1ec7n nghi nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&Yacute; th\u1ee9c l&atilde;nh \u0111\u1ea1o, t\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 v&agrave; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n khi\u1ebfn ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i linh ho\u1ea1t v&agrave; c&oacute; kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th&iacute;ch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi t\u1eebng nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i kh&aacute;ch.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Th&ocirc;ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i: Mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdcf fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-el-has-bg fg-text-dark\"><span class=\"fg-bg\"><span data-fg-bg=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;color&quot;,&quot;opacity&quot;:1,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" class=\"fg-bg-layer fg-bg-type-color \" style=\"opacity: 1; background-color: #ffffff;\"><\/span><\/span><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdci fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">T\u1ea6M NH\u00ccN<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdcj fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle l&agrave; kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh.&nbsp;Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph&aacute;t tri\u1ec3n kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n tr&ecirc;n n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, v\u1ecb tr&iacute;, v&agrave; danh ti\u1ebfng c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c ti&ecirc;u chu\u1ea9n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1eadn t&acirc;m \u0111\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch c&oacute; m\u1ed9t kh&ocirc;ng hai cho c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng trong v&agrave; ngo&agrave;i n\u01b0\u1edbc.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng ng\u1eebng n&acirc;ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5&nbsp; v&agrave; t\u1eadp trung t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111&agrave;o t\u1ea1o k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n.&nbsp;Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i l&atilde;nh \u0111\u1ea1o b\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m g\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111&uacute;c r&uacute;t t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c s&acirc;u r\u1ed9ng v&agrave; th\u1ef1c h&agrave;nh m\u1ecdi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em t\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1eadn t&acirc;m, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v&agrave; sang tr\u1ecdng cho Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; L\u1ef0A CH\u1eccN \u0110\u1ea6U TI&Ecirc;N cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb kh&aacute;ch trong qu&aacute; kh\u1ee9, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v&agrave; t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai khi gh&eacute; th\u0103m Th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Ch&iacute; Minh.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdck fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-4 fg-text-dark\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdcn fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">GI\u00c1 TR\u1eca<\/h2><div class=\"ffb-id-48i4pdco fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Lu&ocirc;n \u0111\u1eb7t kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng l&agrave;m trung t&acirc;m &ndash; V\u01b0\u1ee3t l&ecirc;n ti&ecirc;u chu\u1ea9n 5 sao, Cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 sang tr\u1ecdng, Kh&ocirc;ng ng\u1eebng c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u1ea4m &aacute;p &ndash; Th&acirc;n thi\u1ec7n, Quan t&acirc;m, Chuy&ecirc;n nghi\u1ec7p, Tr&aacute;i tim c\u1ee7a S&agrave;i G&ograve;n&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">T&ocirc;n tr\u1ecdng &ndash; Nhanh nh\u1eb9n,T\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7, Th&iacute;ch nghi, Linh ho\u1ea1t cho Nhu c\u1ea7u thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Kh&aacute;ch<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ho&agrave; h\u1ee3p &ndash; Tinh th\u1ea7n l&agrave;m vi\u1ec7c nh&oacute;m h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch, ch&uacute;ng ta l&agrave; L\u1ef0A CH\u1eccN \u0110\u1ea6U TI&Ecirc;N cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng trong Qu&aacute; kh\u1ee9, Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v&agrave; T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Ch&iacute;nh tr\u1ef1c &ndash; Uy t&iacute;n, Ch&acirc;n th&agrave;nh, \u1ea4m &aacute;p v&agrave; T\u1eadn t&acirc;m nh\u01b0 th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n gia \u0111&igrave;nh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Kaizen &ndash; Li&ecirc;n t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn, Thay \u0111\u1ed5i l&agrave; t\u1ed1t, Thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed7i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, Thay \u0111\u1ed5i t&iacute;ch c\u1ef1c, Thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><style>.ffb-id-48i4pdck{ padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 30px;padding-bottom: 30px;padding-left: 30px;}.ffb-id-48i4pdco{ padding-right: 30px;padding-left: 30px;}.ffb-id-48i4pdco ,.ffb-id-48i4pdco:before,.ffb-id-48i4pdco:after,.ffb-id-48i4pdco *,.ffb-id-48i4pdco *:before,.ffb-id-48i4pdco *:after{ color: #797979 !important;}.ffb-id-48i4pdco{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-48i4pdco:before,.ffb-id-